                 to PageTemplateV2 (left side).
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-21  Initial implementation (full nav trail).
     - 2.0.0  2026-03-24  Re-purposed to show category only (Part 3C).
     - 2.1.0  2026-03-24  SWAPPED responsibility: now renders the full
                          AppState.Breadcrumb trail; category moved to
                          PageTemplateV2.
   ===========================================================================
